Bu, kataku

00:17:35.825 --> 00:17:36.598
jangan pergi.

00:17:38.159 --> 00:17:39.419
Ibu, aku sudah bilang...

00:17:48.123 --> 00:17:49.876
Tidak ada yang bisa memisahkan Chikki dariku.

00:17:52.337 --> 00:17:52.990
Bahkan kamu pun tidak.

00:17:54.923 --> 00:17:55.516
Berhenti di sana, Bu.

